item.title: SoftLayer_Network_Service_Vpn_Overrides
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_Service_Vpn_Overrides Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Network_Service_Vpn_Overrides data type contains information relating user ids to subnet ids when VPN access is manually configured. It is essentially an entry in a ‘white list’ of subnets a SoftLayer portal VPN user may access. Local id The internal identifier of the record. Type: integer subnetId The identifier of a subnet accessible by the SoftLayer portal VPN user.
